<ab>
28. but a sharp-edged painting will look too flat.<lb/>
Thus you should strive for the best manner.<lb/>
For example, you must determine the size of a Column<lb/>
And divide its thickness into three. <lb/>
Draw two points  at equal distances between the contour lines,<lb/>
and on the first point create your brightest highlight, <lb/>
and  at the second point, your deepest shadow,<lb/>
with its width correct.<lb/>
</ab>


<ab><margin>left-middle</margin>The old modern pictures looked very flat. </ab>
